{"tid":2071689,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民航處懶理 警員涉違例教滑翔傘 走法律罅","createTime":"2020-06-20T04:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T12:40:46.000Z","uid":228995,"like":54,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a5beca20e1d82856e29ef686478b699e7136b116","tid":2071689,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"《壹週刊》調查發現，曾在示威現場、在制服背心貼上「民族英雄」徽章的警員袁偉傑兼職擔任滑翔傘學校（Hong Kong Paragliding School）的滑翔傘教練，涉嫌在沒有民航處許可證的情況下受酬指導飛行。<br />\n<br />\n按民航處《空運（航空服務牌照）規例》（香港法例第448A）規定，任何人以滑翔傘提供任何航空服務，包括收費雙人滑翔傘飛行、出租滑翔傘及收費指導飛行，需向民航處申請許可證，違例最高刑罰為罰款$500萬及監禁2年。本刊向民航處查詢，處方回覆表示於2019年未有收到任何人士或團體申請許可證，而2020年則收到一宗申請，並正按機制處理申請，暫時還未批出相關許可證。然而，無論記者在其宿舍試堂，甚至是在郊外「睇堂」，袁偉傑清楚提到課程收費，及如何走避法律規定在港進行飛行教學。此外，根據《政府產業管理及有關事務規例》，獲分配宿舍的人員不應把宿舍用作住所以外的用途，故袁偉傑亦涉嫌以公務員宿舍作非法用途。。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_745643_0?fbclid=IwAR37IS-QW4ivkRagO_4f--hkqy72UNEgn2bLHoFmqTarOwwIiuMHkOt-IgM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_745643_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR37IS-QW4ivkRagO_4f--hkqy72UNEgn2bLHoFmqTarOwwIiuMHkOt-IgM&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=9d394c41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_745643_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR37IS-QW4ivkRagO_4f--hkqy72UNEgn2bLHoFmqTarOwwIiuMHkOt-IgM&h=96f63669\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_745643_0?fbclid=IwAR37IS-QW4ivkRagO_4f--hkqy72UNEgn2bLHoFmqTarOwwIiuMHkOt-IgM</a>"},{"pid":"3f990f2a77b286dc34f5d8cc472c1f4fbd8d6558","tid":2071689,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89a246b7316e8b12510926db4e80e641b39bc